# Nov_16_104 二叉树的最大深度

![](https://tva1.sinaimg.cn/large/0081Kckwgy1gkrh5hjkt3j31ae0lc76q.jpg)

``` c++
class Solution {
public:
    int subTreeDepth(TreeNode *node){
        if(!node) return 0;
        return max(subTreeDepth(node->left) , subTreeDepth(node->right)) + 1;
    }

    int maxDepth(TreeNode* root) {
        return subTreeDepth(root);
    }
};
```

递归的思想，分别找左子树和右子树要最大值